FLOW (with Mangle)\
\
Destination is localhost		-	Interface \'97 Mangle/Prerouting \'97 Nat/Prerouting \'97 Routing decision \'97 Mangle/Input \'97 Filter/Input \'97 Local Process\
\
Source is localhost			-	Local Process \'97 Routing Decision \'97 Mangle/Output \'97 Nat/Output \'97 Filter/Output \'97 Mangle/Postrouting \'97 Nat/Postrouting \'97 Interface\
\
Forwarded packets			-	Interface \'97 Mangle/Prerouting \'97 Nat/Prerouting \'97 Routing Decsion \'97 Mangle/Forward \'97 Filter/Forward \'97 Mangle/Postrouting \'97 Nat/Postrouting \'97 Interface\
\
\
\
FLOW DESCRIPTION (with Mangle)\
\
\'97Coming In from network\'97\
Packets coming in from network go through PREROUTING (Mangle, NAT)\
Make a routing decision\
	Decision is localhost - go through INPUT (Mangle, Filter) and hand to local process\
	Decision is to forward - go through FORWARD (Mangle, Filter) then POSTROUTING (Mangle, NAT) and send it out the interface\
\
\'97from Local Process\'97\
take a routing decision then go through OUTPUT (Mangle, NAT, Filter) then POSTROUTING (Mangle, NAT) and send it out the interface \
\
\
\
\
FLOW DESCRIPTION (without Mangle)\
\
Coming in from network for Localhost 	\'97	NAT/PREROUTING and then FILTER/INPUT and then local process\
Coming in from network to be forwarded 	\'97	NAT/PREROUTING and then FILTER/FORWARD  and then NAT/POSTROUTING and send it out the interface\
Coming from Local Process			\'97	NAT/OUTPUT and then FILTER/OUTPUT and then NAT/POSTROUTING and send it out the interface\
\
\
